  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13050305/verbier-group.jpg" alt="Half Price Lift Passes" rel="858,410" /></p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p style="font-size: 18px; color: #023761;"><strong>Two free whole area lift passes for groups of 15 or more </strong></p>
<p>Book a group ski holiday to <a data-udi="umb://document/a0f5a0d90fe3493faa137de4bb419db4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a0f5a0d90fe3493faa137de4bb419db4}" title="Verbier">Verbier</a> for W17/18 season and receive Two Free Lift Passes. Book by 30th November 2017.</p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><strong>Terms and Conditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><span>Applies to new bookings made after 13/07/2017 and applicable to all departures for winter 17/18 season</span>.</li>
<li><span>This offer cannot be combined with any other lift pass offer</span>.</li>
<li><span>Applies to group passes only (cross-country, walker, season, children and families passes excluded)</span>.</li>
<li><span>Must be added at the time of booking your ski holiday. Can be booked online, with our Reservations Team or through your Travel Agent</span>.</li>
<li><span>All prices, offers and availability are correct at time of publishing, are subject to change &amp; availability and can be withdrawn at any time.</span></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
